<div id="review_1262375204" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1262375204" />
    <a title="Elizabeth Robbins" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/14433078-elizabeth-robbins"><img alt="Elizabeth Robbins" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1452027071p2/14433078.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1262375204?book_show_action=true">Apr 23, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Elizabeth Robbins" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Elizabeth Robbins" href="/user/show/14433078-elizabeth-robbins">Elizabeth Robbins</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1262375204" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16495212250547039991">This is an outstanding first book to a series! I mean it, seriously well-crafted novel. There are so many characters, all entangled. A seriously disfunctional group of doctors and nurses, all so stuck in their own plans for a perfect life that none of them see the pain they are causing the others! Pretty dark, and seriously mind-bending, this book easily earned all five stars! I will be reading the rest of the series ASAP.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


